=== 評價 ===
此片的劇本和演員的演出，尤其是[[艾瑪·湯普遜|艾瑪·湯普遜]]和[[湯姆·漢克斯|湯姆·漢克斯]]的部分獲得諸多好評，艾瑪·湯普遜並獲得2013年度各項電影獎的提名。根據[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的237篇專業影評文章，其中186篇給出了「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為78%，[[加權平均數|平均得分]]7分（滿分10分）<ref name="rt">{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/saving_mr_banks_2013/|title=Saving Mr. Banks|publisher=[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]|accessdate=2014-04-02|archive-date=2017-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171127035722/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/saving_mr_banks_2013/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而基於另一影評網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的46篇評論文章，其中32篇予以好評，2篇負評，12篇褒貶不一，平均分為65（滿分100）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/saving-mr-banks|title=Saving Mr. Banks|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|publisher=[[CBS互動|CBS互動]]|accessdate=2013-11-21|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112024316/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/saving-mr-banks|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

英國著名電影評論家{{link-en|馬克·克莫德|Mark Kermode}}給出四顆星（滿分五顆），並評價該片「艾瑪·湯普遜的詮釋『無懈可擊』。將一個不討喜且擁有矛盾情感的角色以自己的方式呈現得讓人喜愛。」<ref>{{cite news|last=Kermode|first=Mark|title=Saving Mr Banks – review|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2013/dec/01/saving-mr-banks-review|accessdate=2013-12-02|newspaper=The Observer|date=2013-11-30|archive-date=2021-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211102051226/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2013/dec/01/saving-mr-banks-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[華爾街日報|華爾街日報]]》的{{link-en|喬·摩根斯登|Joe Morgenstern}}亦讚賞[[柯林·法洛|柯林·法洛]]的優秀表演<ref>{{cite news|last=Morgenstern|first=Joe|title=Review: Saving Mr. Banks|url=http://online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702303932504579253683274985194?mod=WSJ_ArtsEnt_LifestyleArtEnt_6|accessdate=2013-12-13|newspaper=The Wall Street Journal|date=2013-12-12|archive-date=2014-08-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812133817/http://online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702303932504579253683274985194?mod=WSJ_ArtsEnt_LifestyleArtEnt_6|dead-url=no}}</ref>，《[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石]]》雜誌的{{link-en|彼得·特拉維斯 (影評)|Peter Travers|彼得·特拉維斯}}打出三顆星（滿分四顆），稱讚演員的優異表現<ref>{{cite news|last=Travers|first=Peter|title=Saving Mr. Banks: Review|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/saving-mr-banks-20131212|accessdate=2013-12-13|newspaper=Rolling Stone|date=2013-12-12|archive-date=2017-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171205123836/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/saving-mr-banks-20131212|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[時代_(雜誌)|時代]]》雜誌的影評人凱特·謬爾同樣高度評價湯普遜和漢克斯的演技<ref name=TimesReview>{{cite news|last=Muir|first=Kate|title=Saving Mr Banks, London Film Festival|url=http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/arts/film/londonfilmfestival/article3899748.ece|accessdate=2013-10-21|newspaper=The Times|date=2013-10-21|archive-date=2017-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170303035735/http://www.thetimes.co.uk/tto/arts/film/londonfilmfestival/article3899748.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

